229
00:18:46.201 --> 00:18:47.330
Ya.

230
00:19:12.491 --> 00:19:14.130
Nyaman, darimananya.

231
00:19:14.701 --> 00:19:16.630
Jelek semua lagi bra-nya.

232
00:19:29.380 --> 00:19:30.511
Dasar.

233
00:19:40.090 --> 00:19:43.161
