498
00:40:47.461 --> 00:40:49.921
Kenapa ponselmu mati?

499
00:40:49.921 --> 00:40:51.091
Kau meneleponku?

500
00:40:55.160 --> 00:40:56.560
Ponselku ketinggalan di rumah.

501
00:40:56.861 --> 00:41:00.131
Makanya itu, kenapa kau melarangku
pergi ke rumahmu?

502
