00:42:45.711 --> 00:42:46.910
Cantiknya.

528
00:42:50.281 --> 00:42:51.350
Oh, ya?

529
00:42:52.310 --> 00:42:53.450
Ya.

530
00:42:54.981 --> 00:42:56.321
Sangat cantik.

531
00:43:03.091 --> 00:43:06.691
Tapi kenapa kau memberikannya
tiba-tiba?

532
00:43:09.060 --> 00:43:10.361
Setelah dipikir-pikir..,

533
00:43:11.470 --> 00:43:14.001
...aku baru sadar aku tak 
