00:47:54.822 --> 00:47:56.022
Permisi.

583
00:48:02.393 --> 00:48:03.933
Selamat tinggal.

584
00:48:06.302 --> 00:48:07.402
Ya.

585
00:48:18.543 --> 00:48:19.882
Pesanannya belum datang?

586
00:48:25.022 --> 00:48:26.322
Antingnya cocok.

